msg: C(interface has 'in' ACL applied => interface has 'out' ACL applied)
C(interface has 'out' ACL applied => interface has 'in' ACL applied)
C(ACL covers interface's IP => interface has that ACL applied)
C(interface's IP falls within range ['10.0.2.1', '10.0.2.1'] => ACL aclA applied to the interface)
C(interface's IP falls within range ['10.0.3.1', '20.0.2.1'] => ACL aclB applied to the interface)
C(interface's IP falls within range ['10.0.4.1', '10.0.5.1'] => ACL aclC applied to the interface)
C(interface's IP falls within range ['10.0.4.1', '10.0.4.1'] => ACL aclD applied to the interface)
